## Java vs C++

| Feature        | Java                          | C++                          |
|---------------|-------------------------------|------------------------------|
| Compilation   | Bytecode (JVM)                | Machine code                 |
| Platform      | Platform-independent          | Platform-dependent           |
| Memory Mgmt   | Automatic (Garbage Collector) | Manual (`new` / `delete`)    |
| Pointers      | No direct pointers            | Yes                          |
| OOP           | Mostly pure OOP               | OOP + Procedural             |
| Performance   | Slightly slower               | Faster                       |
| Safety        | More secure                   | Less secure                  |
| Use Cases     | Web, Android, Enterprise      | Games, OS, Embedded systems  |
